title: Annelyse Watch Face
summary: Collection of dials for Android Wear watch
description: Annelyse Watch Face is a collection of dials for your Android Wear watch (Moto 360, LG G Watch R, LG Watch, Samsumg Gear Live ...)Enter the world of this French graphic designer by selecting the Watch Face that suits you best. An astronaut, a fox or maybe a pin-up? Customize your watch according to the time and situation in which you are.New versions will be added regularly.To learn more about Annelyse's work, feel free to discover her website http://annelyse.fr/  and her Facebook page: https://www.facebook.com/AnnelyseAvecUnY
descriptionHTML:
Annelyse Watch Face is a collection of dials for your Android Wear watch (Moto 360, LG G Watch R, LG Watch, Samsumg Gear Live ...)

Enter the world of this French graphic designer by selecting the Watch Face that suits you best.
An astronaut, a fox or maybe a pin-up?
Customize your watch according to the time and situation in which you are.

New versions will be added regularly.

To learn more about Annelyse's work, feel free to discover her website http://annelyse.fr/ and her Facebook page: https://www.facebook.com/AnnelyseAvecUnY
